{"tid":1003051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前練習生爆公司潛規則 想出道就要先陪睡👉💦👌","createTime":"2019-01-31T11:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:24:41.000Z","uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05955beb9a703c467a1d09ddde000549cdda7af5","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"韓國演藝圈競爭激烈，想要出道就要經過重重難關，被選為娛樂公司的練習生只是第一步，要在眾多年輕貌美，才華洋溢的練習生中突圍而出是第二步，但是即使是被選中可以出道了，夢想的現實也可以不是差一步這麼簡單。韓國直播主朴邵崙無論樣貌還是身材都十分亮眼，不過原來她曾經是Fantagio娛樂公司旗下的練習生，只差一步就能出道的時候卻遇上「潛規則」<br />\n<br />\n當年22歲的她被選中成為練習生，接受了訓練約8、9個月，期間除了學習跳舞、演技、唱歌外，甚至還會教導兩性關係及和異性的應對課程。有一天朴邵崙被通知可以出道，她當然非常開心，然而現實總是殘酷的，經紀人卻暗示她想出道必須要「答應一些條件」，除了要跟知名導演陪酒外，甚至還要包養、陪睡，否則就不會有電視或電影演出機會。朴邵崙當下覺得完全不是自己想要的，最終就協議解約了<br />\n<br />\n對於過去發生的一切，從遭到父親家暴、媽媽生病、父母離婚，甚至是不合理的騷擾與對待等，邵崙只想對過去的自己說：「小時候的崙崙，妳辛苦了，在經歷了這麼多事情以後，謝謝妳沒有放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n對於朴邵崙為人生的堅持，許多網民都留言鼓勵，有人認為她能潔身自愛，勇氣可嘉；亦有人大讚朴邵崙即使面對坎坷生活，仍抱正確態度面對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab836d7fb31a9b469dbeb1d48f04bfc340fb99db","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"諗起依家嘅韓國女團...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df4916f62f25acda54c1fffe07f79908c3b8f01","tid":1003051,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57050e91d6750baacbcd5d082dd8c8ad9675eb2c","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df4916f62f25acda54c1fffe07f79908c3b8f01","tid":1003051,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d41db67cf919ba6fac6ea96cb7749a5ae31101","tid":1003051,"uid":132713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaCfUTF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaCfUTF.png&h=a50c54fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38d10ca99c184b2045abd463b99edcefe52da3d6","tid":1003051,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅青春白滑大波長腿偶像，都係要同猥瑣肥叔扑嘢，各位打J前試想像吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e069a6c1e919a1468b663e2ca0fa45cf6b67a64","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d10ca99c184b2045abd463b99edcefe52da3d6","tid":1003051,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅青春白滑大波長腿偶像，都係要同猥瑣肥叔扑嘢，各位打J前試想像吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"出道前之破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f7af1528aa28e5d75691eff07a31441743dd6b","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe4dc133648d9754eb054e4f5265365eb354a54","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30de2f63989a7dfba223bf64249f72c8f5277eb4","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e205356639d8e000efe74cb22cc4f8ed44bd23","tid":1003051,"uid":5190,"like":